{"tid":2195944,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"721事件｜警再拘1「白衣人」涉參與暴動　至今61人被捕　包括47名白衣人","createTime":"2020-09-09T13:27:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T14:08:46.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f107d9ccaacdeedd97027ffd3934e1a34927da8b","tid":2195944,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T13:27:30.000Z","msg":"警方今（9日）就721事件在葵青再拘捕1名33歲男子，他涉嫌「參與暴動」及「串謀有意圖而傷人」正被扣留調查。據悉，被捕男子是「白衣人」。警方至今就721事件累計共拘捕61人，包括47名白衣人及14名非白衣人包括立法會議員林卓廷。<br />\n<br />\nsource: 01"},{"pid":"5029fc33a457806e0b4e8f746835a6d7d2eb713f","tid":2195944,"uid":13193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T13:27:45.000Z","msg":"1個"},{"pid":"b0249e52a78885d929958e5be7430e4894b538fb","tid":2195944,"uid":13193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T13:28:04.000Z","msg":"拉到2046 全部冇罪"},{"pid":"347900da561148f73383bd7df18a4542da8c3006","tid":2195944,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5029fc33a457806e0b4e8f746835a6d7d2eb713f","tid":2195944,"uid":13193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T13:27:45.000Z","msg":"1個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T13:28:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3475277cd91ac74314db73f5fd06ccfef2e980bf","tid":2195944,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0249e52a78885d929958e5be7430e4894b538fb","tid":2195944,"uid":13193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T13:28:04.000Z","msg":"拉到2046 全部冇罪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T13:28:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face